{"tid":1283892,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[記住］唔係「我唔知」，係「我無嘢講」","createTime":"2019-07-04T03:09:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T04:44:32.000Z","uid":59815,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae064f9084e5fee54af3ee4c8d5b6392e7237c46","tid":1283892,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:09:48.000Z","msg":"警犬問：「你知唔知發夢、野餐、香討係咩？」<br />\n<br />\n警犬問：「612當晚你響唔響金鐘？」<br />\n<br />\n警犬問：「你係唔係香討會員？」<br />\n<br />\n以上問題，好多傻仔會以為答「唔知」、「唔係」就無事。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實「唔知」都係一項資料，香討係香港最大討論區，你有無理由唔知？係咪講大話？你係咪無誠信？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n毅進仔還毅進仔，佢地就係學依d野，佢地依方面既幻想、腦補力，根本係連登級數。<br />\n<br />\n總之，一定係答<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我無嘢講！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cb20cf3d474364e492d2319d97cdd676f42d0829","tid":1283892,"uid":259636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"5e3a4100ed8a227d8e0ed9d2f5432ef059264ff0","tid":1283892,"uid":59815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:21:27.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講，我要見律師"},{"pid":"76ab868d0139ee37f866868f219e0706e666ccd7","tid":1283892,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:26:49.000Z","msg":"其實啲狗可唔可以講類似：「你冇嘢講我當你係㗎喇」嗰啲說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n=======================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hdc9J9o.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhdc9J9o.gif&h=43888cd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"985aeb19f3b383f9a26087518c9725f8a954efaf","tid":1283892,"uid":59815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"76ab868d0139ee37f866868f219e0706e666ccd7","tid":1283892,"uid":128472,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:26:49.000Z","msg":"其實啲狗可唔可以講類似：「你冇嘢講我當你係㗎喇